comment: After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor that Pachulia (MIL) was the last player to touch the ball before it went OOB was upheld and CLE was awarded possession.
Pachulia (MIL) sets the screen on Irving (CLE) and gives him the opportunity to stop and/or change direction.
Shumpert's (CLE) contact does not affect Carter-Williams' (MIL) shot.
Dudley (MIL) commits a take foul on Irving (CLE).
